c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both IFTTT and Levity share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. On the other hand, Levity uniquely offers Team Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, IFTTT holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 10/10, while Levity scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, IFTTT offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Levity's starting price of $49/mo. IFTTT has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Levity does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
